Obtaining FFmpeg Source Code:
------------------------------
The complete source code for the version of FFmpeg used in this project can
be obtained from:

1. Official FFmpeg releases: https://ffmpeg.org/download.html
2. Alpine Linux package sources: https://git.alpinelinux.org/aports/
3. Alpine package information: Run `apk info -a ffmpeg` in Alpine container

To extract the specific version used in the container:
```bash
podman run --rm alpine:3.21 sh -c "apk add --no-cache ffmpeg && ffmpeg -version"
```

Note: This project uses FFmpeg as an external binary executable, not as a
linked library. The wrapper scripts in this repository (launch-transcode.sh,
generate-hls.sh) are licensed separately under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

